CryptoPhunks is an NFT project created in July 2021, it is the punk version of CryptoPunks. 

After being censored from the largest NFT platforms and abandoned by the original devs, a renegade group of community builders took it upon themselves to create their own Phunk marketplace. 

Since launch in November 2021, NotLarvaLabs.com has seen over $50M USD in total volume. 

Phunks are Punks facing left, we are flipping the corporate status quo and creating a truly Web3 paradigm through conceptual art. 

We celebrate the self governance of cryptocurrency and embrace community owned platforms. 

This is the essence of decentralization. The blockchain's truth and ability to empower will not be stopped. Be Phree, Be Phunky.

The Laika League is a collection of randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. Our collection consists of 10,000 Laikas who come with all sorts of different outfits, eyes, hairstyles, hats, and more. Each one is entirely unique; no two Laikas look alike! 

On the morning of November 3rd, 1957, a new carbon-based life form appeared on the radars of all the extraterrestrial civilizations monitoring the galaxies. The previously quiet planet of Earth had just launched one of their life forms - a stray dog named Laika - into orbit for the first time. Across the galaxy, Earth was lauded for this first attempt into space travel. It was an expected yet monumental first step in exploring the cosmos for the young planet. 

To some, this significant launch and Laika’s story came to symbolize the spirit of exploration, and they decided to form a club of sorts in commemoration of Laika and her sacrifice. Across the universe, these Laika League members love to support an underdog.
